data.description: Wonderful, spacious home for a growing family or for a multi-generational family. Main floor is perfect with 3BR/2.5 baths, living room, separate dining room, eat-in kitchen, and primary ensuite. Kitchen is spacious, with pantry and access to garage. Downstairs has a kitchenette, two living spaces, a media room, one BR, one large bath, and another room that can be a 5th BR if needed. There's also a workshop in basement with a roll-up garage door for lawn equipment or that special "car" that needs its own space. Upstairs is an attic with floored space for additional storage. The back yard is huge and flat, perfect for kids and pups to run and play. HOA fee is $225 per quarter and amenities include pool, clubhouse, tennis courts, playground, and front gates at entrance. Inside photos coming soon!!
